<H1><A NAME="SECTION00010000000000000000"></A> <A NAME="freezecntr"></A>
<BR>
The Freeze Counter Block <SPAN  CLASS="textit">(freeze_cntr)</SPAN>
</H1> <SPAN  CLASS="textbf">Block Author</SPAN>: Aaron Parsons 
<BR><SPAN  CLASS="textbf">Document Author</SPAN>: Aaron Parsons 
<H2><A NAME="SECTION00011000000000000000">
Summary</A>
</H2>A freeze counter is an enabled counter which holds its final value (regardless of enables) until it is reset.

<P>

